      <div class="service-card">
        <h3 class="service-card__title">Digital Accessibility Audits</h3>
        <p class="service-card__description">Manual testing of your website, LMS, PDFs, and documents using real screen readers &mdash; not just automated tools.</p>
        <ul class="service-card__features">
          <li>Testing with NVDA, JAWS, and VoiceOver</li>
          <li>Desktop, tablet, and mobile testing</li>
          <li>Full documentation with screenshots and screen recordings</li>
          <li>Prioritized list of every barrier found</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="service-card__case-study">Case Study: 360 Articulate Courses VoiceOver Manual Testing</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3 class="service-card__title">VPAT Writing</h3>
        <p class="service-card__description">Full WCAG 2.1 or 2.2 AA conformance documentation.</p>
        <ul class="service-card__features">
          <li>Documents supported, partially supported, and not supported criteria</li>
          <li>Updated after remediation, when needed</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="service-card__case-study">Case Study: American College of Physicians (MKSAP LMS)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3 class="service-card__title">PDF &amp; Document Remediation</h3>
        <p class="service-card__description">Making your existing PDFs, Word documents, PowerPoints, and forms fully accessible and screen-reader ready.</p>
        <ul class="service-card__features">
          <li>Tagging, reading order, alt text, and document titles</li>
          <li>Fillable form accessibility</li>
          <li>Email newsletter accessibility</li>
          <li>Microsoft Word and Google Docs export setup</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3 class="service-card__title">Remediation Roadmaps</h3>
        <p class="service-card__description">After your audit, we deliver a clear, prioritized action plan your team can actually use.</p>
        <ul class="service-card__features">
          <li>Fixes ranked by user impact and implementation complexity</li>
          <li>Written for developers and non-technical staff</li>
          <li>Includes timeline recommendations</li>
          <li>Follow-up review available after remediation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
